=====================================
          FULL PHRASES LIST
=====================================


 PHRASE  |       MEANING
---------|--------------------------------------------
 "exit"  | activates when user exits map/zone type
 "enter" | activates on load/wrap/enter/first interact
 "kill"  | non-player enemy/mini-boss/boss killed
 "death" | non-player NPC killed
 "squash"| non-player user killed
 "XYZ"   | player user killed
 "pick"  | user picks up or activates enemy/boss
 "acts"  | user activates (no touch) enemy/boss
 "touch" | left touches right; events as activator
 "user"  | any non-player + active user
 "jim"   | non-player non-active user
 "sarah" | active user only
 "bob"   | non-enemy (NPCs/non-player/active user)
 "obj"   | non-weapon objects
 "weap"  | weapons
 "armed" | armor
 "arm"   | human arm/limb
 "speed" | increase speed
 "faster"| increase attack speed
 "slower"| decrease attack speed
 "slow"  | decrease speed
 "glue"  | lock creature/object temporarily
 "hot"   | burn temporarily; no-spread
 "cold"  | frost damage; slows over time; no-spread
 "froze" | ice damage; lock + multiply; spreads
 "flame" | fire + burn multiply; spreads
 "drop"  | droppable; event activator on drop
 "xplode"| explodable corpse/enemy/object; activator
 "burp"  | explodes target; activator
 "burpee"| user gains fitness
 "slothee"| user loses fitness
 "plop"  | user drops; *plop* forces drop
 "wrap"  | user enters without door/opening (no death)
 "parw"  | user exits without door/opening (no death)
 "par"   | completes goal within last 5 seconds

=====================================
  Phrases trigger events/actions.
  Pair with symbols (e.g., 'Q'/'I' waypoints).
=====================================
